name: Chocolate Brown Faux Leather Purse
description:
Brand: Air Express
Item Name (Code): Chocolate Brown Faux Leather Purse (CB100)
Description:
Very versatile handbag with a detachable long shoulder strap. Made of soft and durable faux leather. One main compartment, three front zippers, and one back zipper.
Ideal for use as a schoolbag (can fit binders).
